# NorDug Presentation - Project Structure

## Active Content (Edit Here)

```
Presentation-HTML/
├── index.html          # Main Reveal.js slideshow – primary delivery
├── speaker-notes.md    # Full narrative per slide
├── topic-bullets.md    # Quick reference bullets
├── diagrams/           # Mermaid .mmd → .svg
│   ├── config.json     # Dark theme, #FF6B35 accent
│   ├── *.mmd           # Source diagrams
│   └── *.svg           # Rendered diagrams
└── images/             # dEdge logo, etc.
```

## Legacy / Reference

- **_old/** – Archived docs, old PowerPoint, previous versions
- **create_presentation.py** – Generates PowerPoint (.pptx) from hardcoded Python
- **Create-Presentation.ps1** – PowerShell version of same

## Ignore

- **Do not** read, edit, search, or reference **\_old/** – treat it as out of scope for all agent and tool actions.

## Primary vs Secondary

- **Primary:** HTML presentation (index.html) – used for NorDug delivery
- **Secondary:** PowerPoint scripts exist but are not the main output
- When updating content, prioritize **Presentation-HTML/** files
